title: Week 10 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Weekend Reactions - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/15
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 10! Which surprising studs have staying power, and which bad performances are the most concerning? Plus, injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 15th, 2021.

 (05:55) - NFL News
